oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Gary Everton receives the Spirit of the District Award in Nashville
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Woodcuts (prints); skylines; fund raising;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (purple and green on white) announcing Gary Everton receiving the Spirit of the District Award at The District's 31st Annual Progressive Party, a celebration of downtown Nashville. Poster features a woodcut of the Nashville skyline. Event helps fund community projects in the three historic districts and their surrounding areas: Broadway, 2nd Ave/Riverfront, and Printer's Alley, collectively called The District.
